com.google.gcloud.bigquery

Class ViewInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gcloud.bigquery.BaseTableInfo
      • com.google.gcloud.bigquery.ViewInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ViewInfo
extends BaseTableInfo
    Google BigQuery View Table information. BigQuery's views are logical views, not materialized views, which means that the query that defines the view is re-executed every time the view is queried.
    See Also:
    Views, Serialized Form
